Running the code:
  Pseudo-distributed mode:
	1. Set environment variable MR_INPUT to the directory which contains the data files.
	2. Run '. ./env.sh' to set the HADOOP_CONF_DIR to ./.hadoop
	3. Use './run.sh -full-pd' to run the code.

  EMR mode:
	1. Set environment variable MR_INPUT to the directory which contains the data files.
	2. Use './run.sh -full-emr' to run the code.
